LearnMoreModal.sessionLogText: Munthu wogwiritsa ntchito akatsekula chipangizo, nthawi yomwe wakhalapo komanso zomwe waphunzira zimasungidwa. Nthawi iliyonse imene wogwiritsa ntchito watsekula chipangizo imasungidwa ndipo izi zikuphatikizanso kagwiritsidwe ntchito kosadziwika mwini kumene kwachitika popanda munthu wina kulowa pa Kolibri.
LearnMoreModal.summaryLogText: Munthu akhoza kuona zinthu zimodzimodzi nthawi zingapo. Failo ino imasunga nthawi yonse imene munthu waona zinthu komanso mmene munthuyo akuchitira ndiponso zimene wakwanitsa kuchita. Timachita zimenezi mwina potengera maulendo amene munthuyo waona zinthuzo. Sitisunga zimene munthu waonaasanalowe pa pulofailo.
